Noya
========
Noya is a live multitouch sequencer

Requirements
------------
In order to build noya, you need header files and libs of:
 - scons
 - libsndfile
 - libsamplerate
 - clutter (>= 0.8)
 - portaudio (>= 0.19)

For Ubuntu Hardy, you can do

apt-get install scons liblo-dev libsndfile-dev libsamplerate-dev libportaudio19-dev libclutter-0.8-dev

(for libportaudio19-dev and libclutter-0.8-dev, make sure you have "deb http://debian.o-hand.com hardy/" in your /etc/apt/sources.list)

Building and installation
-------------------------
After extracting the dist tarball, run:

  scons

Running noya
------------
Just run:

 ./noya

Troubleshooting
---------------
Noya is in development, no stable version is released yet.
If you have bugs or features, open a ticket on :

 http://noya.txzone.net/


